This is how to is_sorted of lst:
   Remember that n is lst's length
   When n is less than 2, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      When item i in lst is more than item j in lst, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
